      serialVersionUID:
      3458910199790033297L

      • Serialized Fields

        • id

          Long id

        • name

          String name
          Category name - which is unique for a given installation

        • isRegisterable

          boolean isRegisterable
          boolean flag indicating is the members created out of this category are registerable members i.e. to which users can register to

        • isSubmittable

          boolean isSubmittable
          boolean flag indicating is the members created out of this category are submittable members i.e. to which users can submit their assignments to

        • parentCategory

          Category parentCategory
          Parent Category in the category hierarchy tree

        • childCategories

          Set<E> childCategories
          List of children categories to which this category is parent category - currently we only support single parent i.e. a node cannot have multiple parent categories

        • attributes

          Set<E> attributes
          Attributes list which store extra information about this category

        • members

          Set<E> members
          list of members which were created out of this category

        • cmsFolderPath

          String cmsFolderPath
          CMS folder path

        • isRegisterable

          boolean isRegisterable
          boolean flag indicating if this member is registerable member i.e. to which users can register to

        • isSubmittable

          boolean isSubmittable
          boolean flag indicating if this member is submittable members i.e. to which users can submit their assignments to

        • category

          Category category
          Category from which this member is created from

        • parentMember

          Member parentMember
          parent member of this member in the member hierarchy tree

        • childMembers

          Set<E> childMembers
          list of all children members of this member in the member hierarchy tree

        • attributes

          Set<E> attributes
          List of attributes of this member

        • posts

          Set<E> posts
          List of posts for this forum member - kept for future reference - when a Discussion Forum member functionality is implemented

        • userToMemberMappings

          Set<E> userToMemberMappings
          User to Member registration mapping - with their other attributes like registration dates, their role, the registration status, etc.

        • isFinalEvaluated

          boolean isFinalEvaluated
          This flag keeps track if final evaluations are calculated for each individual submitted document from their possibly multiple evaluations. This flag will be made true when Coductor clicks on "disseminating grades" to students // or while calculating fairness of grades - currently its done during "disseminating grades" to students.

        • finalEvalType

          EvalType finalEvalType
          The default EvalType - for final Evaluation calculation for submitted documents; This can be changed while - a) Disseminating grades to students or b) while calculating fairness of grades IMP - Currently it is done - while Disseminating grades to students, as fairness calculation is a future work of this project

        • activationStatus

          MemberStatusType activationStatus
          Member activation status - if this member is active or inactivated

        • submissions

          Set<E> submissions
          All submitted documents for this submittable member

      serialVersionUID:
      1407366847843408348L

      • Serialized Fields

        • id

          Long id

        • submittedForMember

          Member submittedForMember
          Member reference for which this document is submitted for

        • submittedBy

          Set<E> submittedBy
          Users list who are authors of this document; as there can be multiple authors for a single document

        • evaluators

          Set<E> evaluators
          Evaluators list who all evaluated this document

        • evaluations

          Set<E> evaluations
          Evaluations done for this document; Each evaluation is done by independent evaluator

        • finalEvaluation

          Evaluation finalEvaluation
          Unidiretional one-to-one mapping for final Evaluation of this document Final Evaluation of document can be average of multiple evaluations done by multiple reviewers or evaluators

        • submittedFromRemoteAddress

          String submittedFromRemoteAddress
          Remote machine IP address from where this document was uploaded

        • submittedOnTimestamp

          Date submittedOnTimestamp
          Document submission Timestamp

        • filename

          String filename
          Filename of submitted document

        • contentType

          String contentType
          Content Type (MimeType) of submitted document

        • cmsDocId

          String cmsDocId
          CMS document id of submitted document; As each submitted document will be stored into underlying CMS using CMIS APIs; So node-id of this document from CMS

        • cmsDocContentUrl

          String cmsDocContentUrl
          CMS document content URL of submitted document - using this URL we can stream or download actual contents of document anywhere (but not without using CMS access credentials)

        • cmsDocumentPath

          String cmsDocumentPath
          Path of document in CMS

        • cmsDocVersion

          String cmsDocVersion
          Version of document in CMS; Whenever there is a resubmission it will stored as a new version of document i.e. All versions of a given submission will be saved into CMS and only latest version will be referred into SMS for evaluation;
